Rotimi Amaechi, minister of transportation, was on Saturday turbaned Dan Amanar Daura by the Daura Emirate Council in Katsina state. The conferment of the title, according to the emirate council, is in recognition of the achievements recorded by the minister in the transport sector. Below are pictures from the event. <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-659054" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image00001-1024x683.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="600" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-659055" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image00003-1024x683.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="600" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-659057" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image00005-683x1024.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="1024" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-659058" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image00007-683x1024.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="1024" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-659059" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image00009-683x1024.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="1024" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-659063" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image00006-1024x715.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="628" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-659061" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image00002-1024x951.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="836" /> <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-659060" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/image00011-683x1024.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="1024" />